THE INFRINGING PAGE/MATERIAL IDENTIFIED BELOW IS INDEXED AND PRESENT IN YOUR SEARCH ENGINE AND I HEREBY DEMAND THAT YOU ACT EXPEDITIOUSLY TO REMOVE THE PAGE FROM YOUR INDEX AND ALL CACHED OR ARCHIVED COPIES OF THE PAGE FROM YOUR SERVERS.

Note that in some cases the pages/material may have been removed after the sending of this notice but prior to your review.
